{"word":"G2300 - θεάομαι - theáomai - theh-ah'-om-ahee - Behold","slug":"G2300","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θεάομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>theáomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>theh-ah'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Behold"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - theaomai</b> - <i>theh-ah'-om-ahee</i><p/>A prolonged form of a primary verb; to <i>look</i> closely at, that is, (by implication) to <i>perceive</i> (literally or figuratively); by extension to <i>visit</i>: - behold, look (upon), see. Compare <a href=\"#/G3700\">G3700</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2334\">G2334</a>, <a href=\"#/G2529\">G2529</a>, <a href=\"#/G3705\">G3705</a>, <a href=\"#/G3706\">G3706</a>, <a href=\"#/G3707\">G3707</a>, <a href=\"#/G3708\">G3708</a>, <a href=\"#/G4308\">G4308</a>, <a href=\"#/G517\">G517</a>"}]}